{"tid":1651150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警最新風向：支持和理非 反對一切暴力行為 同破壞香港法治的暴徒割席","createTime":"2019-10-13T09:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T17:50:15.000Z","uid":266286,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"695c6327ff0857b81569ec7340de418059f9b59f","tid":1651150,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:04:36.000Z","msg":"事源岩岩碌碌下ig睇下依家咩情況<br />\n咁我不嬲會碌埋comment<br />\n睇下班腦殘藍絲會講啲乜<br />\n順便笑鳩佢地<br />\n咁岩就比我睇到立場新聞其中一個post<br />\n有條友既留言好奇怪<br />\n佢唔同平時d藍絲咁開口埋口就廢青收錢<br />\n反而佢係針對緊記者：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M1p3dZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1p3dZa.png&h=b27c6ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我就唔係好明究竟<br />\n警犬眼罩比人扔左落狗屎箱既報導有咩咁唔中立<br />\n所以就禁落佢個profile睇：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqaFgew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqaFgew.png&h=8774a657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一句就係：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">支持和理非 反對一切暴力行為 同破壞香港法治的暴徒割席</span><br />\n再睇埋佢既following:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/715t9AK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F715t9AK.png&h=d75e6670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87hwnVL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87hwnVL.png&h=83b58b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5V2uAM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5V2uAM.png&h=a4ce34dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩邊既人都有<br />\n<br />\n咁你可能話，咁人地可能真係想吸收吓多方面既資訊呢？<br />\n但係唔好意思 <br />\n靜係睇佢icon<br />\n你都會知依個係個會對示威者去人性化既極深藍ac<br />\n而且你見到佢明顯特登開個新既ig account出黎<br />\n靜係follow反送中既ig<br />\n試問一個真係個關心香港 支持和理非 同時覺得自己睇野好全面既人 會唔會咁樣做？？？<br />\n<br />\n先唔講佢地咁做可以幫藍絲陣營刷follower+留言洗地，從而製造藍絲陣營支持者多既假象。<br />\n<br />\n究竟佢地搞咁多野既主要目的係咩？<br />\n點解要深藍扮支持和理非割席勇武？<br />\n<br />\n係因為佢地想係我地到帶風向！<br />\n佢地想我地吹和理非風，休息風，內鬥互屌風！<br />\n佢地想大多數人同勇武割席！<br />\n佢地想令革命最後步雨革後塵！<br />\n<br />\n因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對家</span></span>依家知道<br />\n要贏 勇武係必要既屬性<br />\n而且勇武比起和理非 更加可以更有效咁打擊到政府<br />\n佢地知道和理非係佔大多數<br />\n知道依單野萬一和理非同勇武<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割 不篤 不分</span></span><br />\n我地係絕對會贏！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港！</span></span>"},{"pid":"44b726b70b8bac008915e3cf52fe9418c6fe409a","tid":1651150,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c93288ce8acad703fe36d4ee51499a7e941fec7","tid":1651150,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:06:42.000Z","msg":"警要新仔幫上頭及大陸武警嘅罪行頂罪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651133</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3383a16ccb378a80b60e81b8a9c546bd58a9943","tid":1651150,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"[即時] RTHK直播 TM 有架康文署貨van有狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1650940/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1650940/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卧狗係新都會優品360捉手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1650958/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1650958/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b713d03479ef317ae62f7df0ad3c4f3475f7023","tid":1651150,"uid":104161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"b10d5f3af7bbc3390e6182fef76e4f64c22c1207","tid":1651150,"uid":123765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"report佢啦"},{"pid":"f25e3fd8603e86f194ab58fd9b54097d7dc693bf","tid":1651150,"uid":3